Text: Hi logros, thanks much for sharing! I was wondering if you might have Gyo volumes 1 & 2 or Tomie volumes 1 & 2 both by Junji Ito.
Hi again logros, please ignore my previous comment, a friend had both of the animes I was looking for so I no longer need them.

oh well i have allready done all the pre-release work on them so il upload them anyway, hopefully someone else will enjoy them. :)

btw its manga not anime. -_-

This was an awesome serie!
I think I never laughed so hard of a manga serie so much as I did with Angel Densetsu.
Both warming and comedic.

Thank you logros13 for uploading this masterpiece.

Very good quality too.
